# CODEOWNERS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Defines who is automatically requested for review when PRs touch these paths.
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner> [<owner> ...]
#
# Rules are matched top-to-bottom; the last matching rule wins.
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global fallback — infra team reviews all changes
*                           @Decentral-America/infra

# Terraform configuration — requires infra lead sign-off
/terraform/                 @Decentral-America/infra

# Bootstrap script — critical; changes affect ALL new server provisions
/terraform/scripts/         @Decentral-America/infra

# GitHub Actions workflows — security-sensitive; CI/CD changes need review
/.github/                   @Decentral-America/infra

# Docker Compose service definitions — affects running containers
/compose/                   @Decentral-America/infra

# Security policy — requires security team review
SECURITY.md                 @Decentral-America/infra
